text.__SUMMARY__: Sphagnum novo-caledoniae is a species of plant in the Sphagnaceae family. It is endemic to New Caledonia.  Its natural habitat is rivers.
text.References: Bryophyte Specialist Group 2000.  Sphagnum novo-caledoniae.   2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species.   Downloaded on 23 August 2007.
